  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Implementing Push Notifications**\n\nI\'m currently focused on integrating a push notification system into the Permit to Work application. My primary objective is to ensure that users receive immediate alerts via their devices whenever a permit is submitted for approval or requires any form of action from them. This will streamline the workflow by providing timely updates.\n\n\n**Analyzing Notification Implementation**\n\nI\'m now delving into the implementation details of the push notification system, specifically for the Permit to Work app. My focus has shifted towards leveraging native browser APIs, specifically the Web Notifications API, instead of relying on a real-time server. This seems the most streamlined way to show immediate alerts when a permit needs approval.\n\n\n"
